basics.label: Customer Service Specialist
basics.summary: Enthusiastic and hard-working Customer Service Specialist looking to obtain a position in an environment where my skills are valued and can benefit the organization. Dedicated, focused and excels at prioritizing, completing multiple tasks simultaneously and following through to achieve project goals. Seeking a challenging role of increased responsibility and authority.
